res = gp_minimize(bench3, [(-2.0, 2.0)], x0=[0.0], noise=1e-08, n_calls=8,
    n_random_starts=3, random_state=1)
x_min, f_min = expected_minimum(res, random_state=1)
x_min2, f_min2 = expected_minimum(res, random_state=1)
assert f_min <= res.fun
assert x_min == x_min2
assert f_min == f_min2
